sentences.english: I had some flat plate end caps welded up to use as legs and mold material blockages.
sentences.chinese: 我有一些平板端蓋焊接起來用腿和模具材料的淤塞。

sentences.english: Sand has silted up the river delta .
sentences.chinese: 泥沙把這條河的三角洲淤塞了。

sentences.english: And imported water hyacinth plants are choking some parts of the Yangtze River and the Pearl River.
sentences.chinese: 而進口的水葫蘆正在淤塞長江和珠江的部分河段。

sentences.english: The canal would soon fill up with mud if not regularly dredged.
sentences.chinese: 這條運河如果不經常疏浚，就會淤塞。

sentences.english: Sanmenxia was the nation's pride until its reservoir silted up.
sentences.chinese: 在水庫被淤塞之前，三門峽一直是這個民族的驕傲。

sentences.english: The harbour silted up a year ago.
sentences.chinese: 該港口一年前就淤塞了。
